ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of CLAIRE M.C. KENNEDY of Toronto, Ottawa, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Dominique Hamel, whose term will expire, effective June 21, 2025.
